official_title: A bill to return the privately built and maintained reservoir known as Lake Oswego, Oregon, to its traditional status as a nonnavigable water of the United States.

summary.text: Declares the reservoir known as Lake Oswego and its canals in the city of Lake Oswego, Oregon, to be nonnavigable waters of the United States.
